opinions.text:
HAMITER, Justice.
For the reasons assigned in the cause entitled Weiss v. Board of Commissioners for Pontchartrain Levee District, 238 La. 419, 115 So.2d 804, the judgment appealed from is affirmed.
McCALEB, J., dissents in part for the written reasons given in No. 44,618.
opinions.author: HAMITER, Justice.
